=== Cultural properties / Natural monuments ===
In {{ill|lt=1973|Q2477|WD=Q2477|1=1973}} ({{ill|lt=Shōwa|Q327567|WD=Q327567|1=Shōwa era}} 48), three items were designated cultural properties by Osaka Prefecture.
*Honden - built in 1595. {{ill|lt=Japanese cypress|Q917187|WD=Q917187|1=Chamaecyparis obtusa}} bark roof, with chidori {{ill|lt=hafu gable|Q4881511|WD=Q4881511|1=Bargeboard}}.
*Stone komainu - one pair, {{ill|lt=Kyōwa|Q960763|WD=Q960763|1=Kyōwa}} 4
*Stone lanterns - from {{ill|lt=Hōreki|Q1194397|WD=Q1194397|1=Hōreki}} 4 to {{ill|lt=Kaei|Q1146125|WD=Q1146125|1=Kaei}} 2
